## Open Components — MIT License

The following components are released under the MIT License:

- Game integration plugins (SKSE, F4SE, and other game-specific plugins)
- HTTP client libraries and API interface definitions
- Flask server scaffolding and endpoint routing
- Model provider interface (abstract base classes)
- Model routing infrastructure (dual-model, fallback logic)
- Response caching layer
- Build systems and configuration templates
- Documentation describing integration and deployment

