## Proprietary Components — All Rights Reserved

The following components are proprietary and all rights are reserved
by Gamemodes:

- Psychological modeling system and algorithms
- Prompt templates, prompt architecture, and prompt construction logic
- NPC profile schemas and psychological profile definitions
- Training data (generated, curated, and seed examples)
- Training methodology and data generation pipelines
- Quality scoring criteria and evaluation frameworks
- Fine-tuned model weights and adapter files
- Trigger mapping systems and state-to-behavior algorithms
- Any file, directory, or module marked with "PROPRIETARY" in its
  header or accompanying documentation

These components may not be copied, modified, distributed, sublicensed,
sold, reverse-engineered, or used to create derivative works without
explicit written permission from Gamemodes.

Access to proprietary components in any Gamemodes repository, whether
public or private, does not constitute a grant of license to use those
components outside of their intended context within the Gamemodes
platform.

