## Identifying Component Classification

Files belonging to open components will contain the following header
where practical:

    // SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
    // Part of Gamemodes — Open Integration Layer

Files belonging to proprietary components will contain the following
header where practical:

    // PROPRIETARY — Gamemodes (Game Model Development Studio)
    // All Rights Reserved. See LICENSE for terms.

If a file does not contain either header, its classification is
determined by the directory it resides in. Consult the project
documentation or contact gamemodes.dev@gmail.com for clarification.

